    • Field Detail

      • rl_connections_activity_device_list_background_layout

        private RelativeLayout rl_connections_activity_device_list_background_layout
        Layout under lv_connections_activity_device_list. RelativeLayout which is displayed in place of the list of devices when it is empty before refreshing by tapping b_connections_activity_refresh_connections_check or the list of devices is in the process of generating after tapping button b_connections_activity_bluetooth_switcher or #b_connections_activity_wireless_switcher. It is also displayed when, after refreshing, there is no devices to display. If so, appropriate text is displayed.

      • pb_connections_activity_refreshing

        private ProgressBar pb_connections_activity_refreshing
        Progress bar that appears in the course of generating the list of devices. This progress bar is an element of rl_connections_activity_device_list_background_layout. It is displayed during searching for connections with devices and generating their list after tapping one of the buttons:
        • b_connections_activity_bluetooth_switcher,
        • b_connections_activity_wireless_switcher,
        • b_connections_activity_refresh_connections_check.

      • lv_connections_activity_device_list

        private ListView lv_connections_activity_device_list
        List of generated connections with other devices. Each generated element consists of fields defined in ElementOfConnectionsList. When empty or not initialized it is not displayed at all (see rl_connections_activity_device_list_background_layout). After generating it displays every element on listOfElements.
        See Also:
        listOfElements, selectedConfig, lv_connections_activity_device_list_visibly

      • b_connections_activity_bluetooth_switcher

        private ImageToggleButton b_connections_activity_bluetooth_switcher
        Button that fires searching for available bluetooth connections.
        • When button is tapped short: It fires execution of GenerateConnectionList that adds to list bluetooth connections which have been found.
        • When button is tapped long: It replaces default type of connections to bluetooth type- when there are default connections stored in Android memory of both types, the priority one is a bluetooth type and after discovering such a connection it is set automatically.
        See Also:
        MultiPlayApplication.setMainNetworkConfiguration(ConnectionsConfigurationClass)

      • b_connections_activity_wireless_switcher

        private ImageToggleButton b_connections_activity_wireless_switcher
        Button that fires searching for available wireless connections.
        • When button is tapped short: It fires execution of GenerateConnectionList that adds to list wireless connections which have been found.
        • When button is tapped long: It replaces default type of connections to wireless type- when there are default connections stored in Android memory of both types, the priority one is a wireless type and after discovering such a connection it is set automatically.
        See Also:
        MultiPlayApplication.setMainNetworkConfiguration(ConnectionsConfigurationClass)
